System Description


Network Simulator                       NS3
Number of Mobile Nodes                  2
Number of Stationary Nodes              1
Relative Speed between the nodes        10 m/s
MAC Protocol                            IEEE 802.11p
MAC Rate                                12Mbps
Ether Type                              WSMP
Channel Type                            CCH
Packet Size                             88 bytes
Data Rate                               CBR (Constant Bit Rate)
Propagation Loss Model                  Nakagami, Log Distance
Simulation Grid                         500m x 100m x 100m
Simulation Time                         100 seconds
